Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:01:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Despite Kaiba's heartless attack against my Partner and the other Mirror Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we just ended up facing Orichalcos Shunoros in their place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now that Kaiba has fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I am fighting this battle all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With all three Barriers of Orichalcos on the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as well as Orichalcos Shunoros...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not sure how I should fight them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a cursed king?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:02:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Revive!\N The Three Legendary Warriors"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that my existence is what will destroy the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh, your cursed spirit has already gained control over the darkness in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an abominable king whom has resurrected in order to lead this world to its demise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last thing I remember is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was being used as Dartz's Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Kaiba's Mirror Force Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you, Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Pegasus!\N -Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly never imagined we would reunite in such a way as this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here, then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get it together, you gu-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heck? It's like all the strength's leavin' my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's been draining our strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... it is the god Dartz spoke of offering us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta get outta here somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way we'll make it out of here is if Dartz is defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's he doing here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} arrived here shortly after we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means my other self is fighting Dartz alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's facing Dartz all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That my other self will beat Dartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that he'll rescue us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before we disappeared from the Duel, he had close to 20000 Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he had the three barriers of the Orichalcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is still hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has the nameless card I entrusted to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he were to use that power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless card...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, in order to create a variety of Duel Monsters cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I traveled all around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherein, I heard tale of the three dragons said to exist among the Duel Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These dragons, whose names were lost ages ago after a massive conflict,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now sleep among the Duel Monsters undisturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a transient yet mysterious existence they hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried tapping into my imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I came up with a hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hypothesis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These dragons are merely their temporary forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their true forms were sealed away by the King of Darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they took on the form of dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nameless dragons are their temporary forms?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is certainly inconceivable for those who view life through the facts of our world's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the microscopic world exists unseen by the naked eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As does the dark void of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with it, existence mankind can only fathom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it is impossible to truly see,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,humans are capable of creating an entire world of possibility through their imaginations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unlimited potential that can alter the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what we call imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! Using our imaginations...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can create our own world within our souls that will cast away the darkness in our hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nameless Pharaoh is one of the Chosen Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith that he will discover the power of that card!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz! I won't be fooled by your words!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore to Black Magician Girl and my partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironheart and Kris also gave me a mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mission," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a thing never existed from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your only {\i1}mission{\i0} is to become\N one of the gears of destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gears of destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The Duel Monsters and your comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as my father and my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of them realized that you are the reason behind the world's destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they blindly put their hopes in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vision you saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the only one who could recall the conflict that took place 10,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Similarly, disaster struck once more 3,000 years ago in Ancient Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying the events I saw were caused by my very existence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying you held no meaning from the very {\i1}start{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie... It's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't believe such nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Pot of Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I draw two cards from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Retrained Elf Swordsman in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For now, I have to withstand his attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't come even close to striking Orichalcos Shunoros!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place an additional reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That finishes my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it is my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the effects of Orichalcos Deuteros!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got 20000 Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Dexia's Attack Power will always rise 300 points higher than the opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this attack is able to pass through your Wall Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you will lose all the Life you possess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Dexia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Retrained Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate! Soul Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By cutting my Life Points in half with this card,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am able to negate the Monster's attack and end the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such reluctance, Nameless Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you had best look around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the comrades that support you have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bond you believe in so much no longer exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What point is there in suffering so much by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it would be in your best interest to carefully examine the situation of this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe you hold any hope of victory the way you are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's got 20000 Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's got the invincible Orichalcos Shunoros on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Along with the three Barriers of Orichalcos...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My hope of victory has already...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are nothing more than a cursed soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What merit could getting back such unsightly memories possibly hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The labyrinth in your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you were to open that meaningless door and regain your lost memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all that would await you is horror and tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh... Your pain and your worries...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings that you have felt over the span of endless time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I alone am the only one capable of understanding your suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The very least you can do is put an end to your fate with your very own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just raise my hand, that fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put an end to all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring your existence back to nil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... nil?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not wish to join your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... I used to be nil...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Simply trapped within the Millennium Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Null, from the very beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I lose them, I have nothing left...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is why I have to vanish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surround him, Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Disappear...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got nothing... left within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Past memories... My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does someone like me who holds no existence have it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something in my heart that can never be erased...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have something like that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I never noticed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep within my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the bonds I've woven with my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a vessel of memories....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not nil...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:13:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I still have the vessel inside of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times it takes... I can still be reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz, allow me to answer you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing everything, why did I cross over 3,000 years of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I brought back into this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because... I was revived in order to protect my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as well as to defeat you and change the future of the world in the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the nameless card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can feel it... In my current state, I can feel the hidden powers of this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I believe in the vision of the future I hold with my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grant me your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legend of Hearts!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:14:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pay 1000 Life Points and offer up a Warrior-Type Monster I have on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who has called us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Us souls still a slumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You call us into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Critias!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let our power fill this place with light!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That{\i0} is the true form \Nof the nameless dragons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cannot be! The Barrier of Orichalcos was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our bonds are absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A barrier of darkness shall not work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the one who gave me this wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to pay you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have now eliminated your untouchable barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timaeus! Attack Orichalcos Aristeros!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Critias!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll now end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Willingly injuring your own Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to lower Shunoros' Attack Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, your Life is nothing but a flickering light in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This does not change the fact that my next attack will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Shunoros! Advance and attack Critias!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Special Effect of Critias!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can absorb the effects of every Trap Card used throughout this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card Critias has absorbed is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Barrier - Mirror Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Critias will reflect the attack sent at him towards every one of the opponent's Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wisdom Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you would manage to defeat Shunoros...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil God Gē.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the strongest servant I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The very moment Orichalcos Shunoros' Attack Power reaches zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can give up 10000 of my Life Points as well as every card in my hand in order to Special Summon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Life Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Life is in turn eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as soon as my servant is destroyed, I automatically accept defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, its Attack Power is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its Attack Power... reached infinity!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was never any hope for the likes of yourself to defeat me from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw your final card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there... even a way to defeat that Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My deck... My Monsters... I will believe in you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Magician Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both us Duel Monster's world and your world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master, you are the only one capable of saving both of our worlds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The promise I made that day... I will uphold it no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card face-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I discard the first ten cards in my deck in order to invoke the Evil God Gē's attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infinity End!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This puts an end to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the beginning of a new history.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cursed soul... now belongs to my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not possible! Your Life...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pity for {\i1}you{\i0}. I just activated a Trap Card in that attack just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activated Relay Soul, to be more precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my Life Points reach zero, Relay Soul Summons a Monster from my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a card that pits the end of this Duel with the selected Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Black Magician Girl is destroyed, I automatically lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the both of us are in the same situation in this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul is now a part of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz! This begins the real battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you truly believe such a level of strength is capable of besting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of infinity lies within my Serpent God Gē, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be affected by your words any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in the bonds I hold with my Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bold front of yours shall end there, Nameless Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impact Revive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:21:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card revives a Monster destroyed this turn and increases their Attack Power by 500 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall choose to place it on the opponent's field!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... revived Timaeus?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Knights are nothing more than meaningless beings when faced with infinite Attack Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as the cost of this effect, I am permitted to enter the Battle Phase once again this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I send ten cards from the top of my deck into the Cemetery!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grant me your power one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serpent God Gē!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infinity End!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vanish from this realm, Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:22:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.79,0:22:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three nameless dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.29,0:23:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So their true forms were the Legendary Knights, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shunoros was beaten. So this is as far as Dartz-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we thought, but he still had a hidden trump!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it's a Monster with infinite Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he defeat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi left his Life with Black Magician Girl against the Serpent God Gē!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will be Yugi and the world's fate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.27,0:23:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Infinite Attack Power: Serpent God Gē"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
